<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>{{ CANDIDATE NAME }} — CV</title>
<style>
  /* ---------- Page setup ---------- */
  @page { size: A4; margin: 0; }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }

  html, body {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    background: #fff;
    font-size: 10pt;
    line-height: 1.45;
  }

  :root {
    /* Customize the accent color to taste. Defaults to dark teal. */
    --accent: #1f3a3d;
    --accent-soft: #2f5559;
    --muted: #666;
    --rule: #c8d4d5;
  }

  /* ---------- Layout ---------- */
  .page {
    width: 210mm;
    min-height: 297mm;
    margin: 0 auto;
    background: #fff;
  }

  /* Header */
  .header {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr;
    align-items: stretch;
    background: var(--accent);
    color: #fff;
  }

  .header .photo {
    width: 200px;
    height: 200px;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center 25%;
    display: block;
    background: #ddd;
  }

  .header .header-text {
    padding: 28px 36px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .header h1 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 30pt;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.3px;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .header .subtitle {
    font-size: 14pt;
    margin-top: 4px;
    font-weight: 300;
    opacity: 0.92;
  }

  .header .contact {
    margin-top: 20px;
    font-size: 10pt;
    opacity: 0.95;
  }

  .header .contact a {
    color: #fff;
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  /* Body */
  .body {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr;
    gap: 28px;
    padding: 24px 32px 28px;
  }

  /* Sidebar */
  .sidebar h3 {
    font-size: 9.5pt;
    margin: 0 0 4px 0;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.4px;
  }

  .sidebar .field {
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    font-size: 9.5pt;
  }

  .sidebar .field .value {
    color: #333;
  }

  .lang-bars {
    display: flex;
    gap: 3px;
    margin-top: 3px;
  }
  .lang-bars .bar {
    height: 4px;
    width: 22px;
    background: #1a1a1a;
    border-radius: 1px;
  }
  .lang-bars .bar.empty { background: #d6d6d6; }

  .sidebar ul.tight {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    list-style: none;
    font-size: 9.5pt;
    color: #333;
  }
  .sidebar ul.tight li { margin-bottom: 2px; }

  .skill-block { margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .skill-block .skill-label {
    font-size: 9pt;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 1px;
  }
  .skill-block .skill-value {
    font-size: 9.5pt;
    color: #1a1a1a;
  }

  /* Main */
  main h2 {
    font-size: 14pt;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0 0 8px 0;
    color: var(--accent);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
    padding-bottom: 6px;
  }
  main h2:not(:first-child) { margin-top: 22px; }

  main section { margin-bottom: 0; }

  .entry {
    margin-top: 14px;
    page-break-inside: avoid;
  }

  .entry .role {
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 10.5pt;
    margin: 0;
    color: #1a1a1a;
  }

  .entry .role .company-accent {
    color: var(--accent-soft);
  }

  .entry .dates {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 9pt;
    margin: 2px 0 6px 0;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .entry p {
    margin: 0 0 4px 0;
    text-align: left;  /* Avoid `justify` — produces word-spacing rivers at this size */
  }

  .entry ul {
    margin: 3px 0 4px 18px;
    padding: 0;
  }
  .entry ul li { margin-bottom: 1px; }

  .entry .stack {
    margin-top: 6px;
    font-size: 9pt;
    color: var(--muted);
  }
  .entry .stack strong {
    color: #333;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .compact-entry { margin-top: 6px; }
  .compact-entry .role { font-size: 10pt; }

  /* Print */
  @media print {
    html, body { background: #fff; }
    .page {
      width: 210mm;
      min-height: auto;
      margin: 0;
      box-shadow: none;
    }
    .entry { page-break-inside: avoid; }
    main h2 { page-break-after: avoid; }
  }

  @media screen {
    body { background: #ececec; padding: 24px 0; }
    .page { box-shadow: 0 2px 14px rgba(0,0,0,0.12); }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="page">

  <header class="header">
    <img class="photo" src="photo.jpeg" alt="{{ CANDIDATE NAME }}">
    <div class="header-text">
      <h1>{{ CANDIDATE NAME }}</h1>
      <div class="subtitle">{{ Identity tagline — keep short and authentic, e.g. "Engineer · Entrepreneur" }}</div>
      <div class="contact">
        {{ phone }} &middot;
        <a href="mailto:{{ email }}">{{ email }}</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="body">

    <aside class="sidebar">
      <div class="field">
        <h3>Date of birth</h3>
        <div class="value">{{ DD/MM/YYYY }}</div>
      </div>

      <div class="field">
        <h3>Nationality</h3>
        <div class="value">{{ nationality }}</div>
      </div>

      <div class="field">
        <h3>Location</h3>
        <div class="value">{{ city · city · city }}</div>
      </div>

      <div class="field">
        <h3>Links</h3>
        <div class="value"><a href="{{ linkedin url }}">{{ linkedin display }}</a></div>
        <div class="value"><a href="{{ other url }}">{{ other display }}</a></div>
      </div>

      <div class="field">
        <h3>Languages</h3>
        <div class="value">{{ Language 1 }}</div>
        <div class="lang-bars">
          <span class="bar"></span><span class="bar"></span>
          <span class="bar"></span><span class="bar"></span>
          <span class="bar"></span>
        </div>
        <div class="value" style="margin-top:6px;">{{ Language 2 }}</div>
        <div class="lang-bars">
          <span class="bar"></span><span class="bar"></span>
          <span class="bar"></span><span class="bar"></span>
          <span class="bar empty"></span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="field">
        <h3>Skills</h3>
        <div class="skill-block">
          <div class="skill-label">{{ Category 1 — e.g. AI }}</div>
          <div class="skill-value">{{ specific tools / frameworks / techniques — comma or middot separated }}</div>
        </div>
        <div class="skill-block">
          <div class="skill-label">Domains</div>
          <div class="skill-value">{{ sectors and functional areas of depth }}</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="field">
        <h3>Hobbies</h3>
        <ul class="tight">
          <li>{{ hobby 1 }}</li>
          <li>{{ hobby 2 }}</li>
          <li>{{ hobby 3 }}</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </aside>

    <main>

      <section>
        <h2>Profile</h2>
        <div class="entry" style="margin-top:8px;">
          <p>{{ ~120-180 words. The most-tailored paragraph in the CV — fork per application. Lead with the candidate's authentic identity. Hit the 2-3 strongest facts. Close with what they're looking for and a values line. Match their actual voice — no buzzwords. }}</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Employment History</h2>

        <div class="entry">
          <p class="role">{{ Role }}, <span class="company-accent">{{ Company }}</span></p>
          <p class="dates">{{ Start }} — {{ End or Present }} · {{ City }}</p>
          <p>{{ 2-5 sentences of substance: what they did, key achievements with numbers, what stands out. Don't make this a job description; make it the story.}}</p>
          <p class="stack"><strong>Stack:</strong> {{ relevant tech if applicable }}</p>
        </div>

        <div class="entry">
          <p class="role">{{ Next role }}, <span class="company-accent">{{ Next company }}</span></p>
          <p class="dates">{{ Start }} — {{ End }} · {{ City }}</p>
          <p>{{ Substance }}</p>
        </div>

        <!-- More entries as needed, reverse chronological -->
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Education</h2>

        <div class="entry compact-entry">
          <p class="role">{{ Degree }} — <span class="company-accent">{{ Institution, City }}</span></p>
          <p class="dates">{{ Year start }} — {{ Year end }}</p>
        </div>

        <div class="entry compact-entry">
          <p class="role">{{ Degree }} — <span class="company-accent">{{ Institution, City }}</span></p>
          <p class="dates">{{ Year start }} — {{ Year end }}</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Internships</h2>

        <div class="entry compact-entry">
          <p class="role">{{ Role }}, <span class="company-accent">{{ Company }}</span> — {{ City }}</p>
          <p class="dates">{{ Start }} — {{ End }}</p>
          <p>{{ Brief description, ideally an interesting story. }}</p>
        </div>
      </section>

    </main>
  </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
